{"html":"<section id=\"appendix\">\n\t\t\t<h2>Sketch Map of the Route from Salamanca to Toledo</h2>\n\t\t\t<figure id=\"illustration-1\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt=\"A map entitled “Sketch Map of the Route from Salamanca to Toledo.” The route highlighted is in southern Spain, and goes via Calvarasa, Albe de Tormes, Horcaja, Piedrahita, Navalacruz, S. Martin de Val de iglesia, Almorox, Escalona, Magueda, and Torrijos.\" src=\"../images/illustration-1.svg\"/>\n\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t</section>"}